description: Deletes a what-if forecast export created using the  CreateWhatIfForecastExport operation. You can delete only what-if forecast exports that have a status of ACTIVE or CREATE_FAILED. To get the status, use the  DescribeWhatIfForecastExport operation.

parameters.name: WhatIfForecastExportArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the what-if forecast export that you want to delete.
